<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stomach-n">stomach <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'stʌmək/    美 /'stʌmək/  </p>
<p>[C] </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-pl-stomachs">1.★ <strong>(pl stomachs) 胃；肚子；腹部：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s unwise to swim on <strong>a full stomach</strong>. 
刚吃完饭不宜游泳。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have a terrible <strong>stomachache</strong>.
我胃/肚子很疼。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>John missed the game because of <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ (胃) pains.  （2009 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. stomach  </p></div>